-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n轉口越南都走唔甩！美國懲罰性關稅打沉鋼鐵商品股 <br />\n<br />\n2017年12月06日<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部宣布，對由越南進口，使用中國基材的耐蝕鋼產品徵199.43%反傾稅及39.05%反補貼稅，冷軋鋼產品則徵265.79%反傾銷稅及265.44%反補貼稅。美商務部稱中國鋼材經越南出口到美國，以規避美國針對中國的懲罰性關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57546732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57546732&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=78b84180\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57546732&h=d49bdb61\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57546732</a>"},{"pid":"093e7bf8d33b03b8070610d427f354d691c96b0a","tid":538349,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"TRADE WAR: US and China relations on BRINK over explosive documents<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/904984/us-china-trade-war-tensions-explosive-documents\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F904984%2Fus-china-trade-war-tensions-explosive-documents&d=FQIZZSg3jStbvmcjSHMLoNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=279c4887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/904984/us-china-trade-war-tensions-explosive-documents</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e28af79495d543260b167db79724ddc1659d3d","tid":538349,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093e7bf8d33b03b8070610d427f354d691c96b0a","tid":538349,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"TRADE WAR: US and China relations on BRINK over explosive documents<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/904984/us-china-trade-war-